segue_dave.line: Prefab Sprout released records for Kitchenware Records, a label founded in 1982, while The Jam broke up in the same year...
segue_dave.explanation: Prefab Sprout released a former album with Kitchenware Records, a record label which was founded in 1982 and The Jam was formed as a band in the same year.
